<br />
3. F**k ADC. Seriously. I don't want it. I don't CARE about it. I wouldn't spend a single AA on it. I'm NOT A FREAKING MAGE! (But saying that, I'm not a darn tank either, yet I have to have 10k+ hp in most high end situations that require charming / mezzing.)
<br />
4. If you want a controllable pet so desperately that does decent DPS - Re-roll as a mage.
<br />
5. Actually remove charm. Dump it, get rid of it. No one will ever let a chanter charm in a raid when you are not able to predict when the pet will turn deadly. I cannot even count the amount of wipes on Tipt named because pet broke half way through.
<br />
6. Now give me my stuns back. Give me back CONTROL.
<br />
7. If we keep charm, and it gets nerfed to hell as proposed.. Then I want charm to be recoded to be fixed duration and that charm can't be debuffed by the mob.
<br />
Since that will never happen.... just get rid of it.
