                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">What would be acceptable to me across the board...
<br />
<ul>
<br />
<li>Remove the exp penalty from charm place it under the same rule as mage pets...
<br />
<li>Extend charm duration either directly in the spell or through mods
<br />
<li>Charm does a dps reduction of 40% so pet is only doing 60 % dmg
<br />
<li>Add a new haste line for charmed pets only have charmed pets ignore normal haste from items and regular casts
<br />
<li>When charm drops so does charm only haste
<br />
<li>All mobs outside of gods, dragons and bosses should be Charmable
<br />
<li>Charm max level should be equal to the level of the spell(ie level 65 spell level 65 cap</ul></span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
